pull_request.body:
# Steps To Test
1. ```git fetch -all```
2. ```git checkout KH_firstticket```
3. go to views > shared > layout and delete line 38, 39 (``` @if (Context.User.Identity.IsAuthenticated) 
                     { ```)  
and delete line 41(```{```)
4. Run app..you should see Sell a Product in the nav bar.  Click and try to submit blank form
5. You should see errors
6.  Go back to layout file and CTRL Z to replace the original lines back and run the program again
7.  You should not see Sell a Product because you are not logged in
